message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $120. I believe it offers significant value at this price.
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I believe I can offer you $100 for the product.
Thanks for your offer, Bob. I'm willing to come down a bit to $110. I believe this is a fair price considering the value this product offers.
Hello Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. I would like to counter with an offer of $105 for the product.
